{
  "stem": "9943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That means without taking them away from work to learn to be nurses, army nurses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was another job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The third, they had to have a committee to decide who needs to get a pension and what kind of a pension, limited pension, or more.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they needed a committee, which was called [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], That's a-- which I was a neurologist.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I was a neurologist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the fourth job is at [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The welfare department was organizing a home for physically handicapped children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They wanted to demonstrate these free health services.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was very enthusiastic about that job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because at the time when I was in this hospital for children in Warsaw when I was learning to be a physician, a pediatric-- a pediatrician for children, the-- we brought them-- a woman brought-- a Jewish woman brought a child very sick with pneumonia.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He needed hospitalization.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she had to-- she needed-- the child needed the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But, in order to leave the child in the hospital, she had to pay for a month stay.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she didn't have money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I, I was on duty at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I decided that she needed hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the rest was not in my hands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, and I didn't have money to pay for her because I would have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they sent her away home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she was raising hell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She was screaming, and there was a policeman standing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the policeman asked her for-- anyway, she had to take this child home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I never forgot that situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So here, they have free health for everybody, without payments.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So naturally that was very appealing to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I was-- I was satisfied.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
